> # Enable at Launch
> ## (Default: Off)
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>   The application will start with backgrounding disabled.
>
> * **On:**  
>   The application will start with backgrounding enabled; it can later be disabled via normal methods.

- - -

> # Stay Enabled
> ## (Default: On)
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>   Backgrounding must be enabled every time the application is minimized.
>
>   Using this setting, one could, for example, use a single press of the Home button to quit the application and a double press to background it.
>
> * **On:**  
>   Once backgrounding has been enabled for the application, it will remain enabled until the user manually disables it - no matter how many times the application is minimized and restored.
